1.  To start front end
    a. npm create vite@latest app_name
    b. npm install -D tailwindcss@3.4.17 postcss autoprefixer
    c. npx tailwindcss init -p
    d. npm install clsx

2.  To start the frontend
    a. npm init -y
    b. npm install express mongoose dotenv
    c. Put the mongoDB url in the .env file
    d. npm install bcrypt

